1. Ona je ušla u njegov sinu* bez poziva. (She entered his room without invitation.)
2. Oni su bili u žalosti kad su čuli o smrti njegovog sinu*. (They were sad when they heard about the death of his son.)
3. On je prošlosti sina* ponovo vratio u život. (He brought the past of his son back to life.)
4. Ona je bila začuđena zbog čudnog ponašanja sinu*. (She was surprised by the strange behaviour of her son.)
5. Ona je bila uzbuđena da čuje sinu* nastupati. (She was excited to hear her son perform.)